  keywords = {Animals,beta-Galactosidase,cancer associated fibroblast,Cancer-Associated Fibroblasts,Carcinoma Large Cell,Cell Cycle Checkpoints,Cell Line Tumor,Cell Movement,Cell Shape,Cellular Senescence,Coculture Techniques,Culture Media Conditioned,Disease Progression,Female,Humans,invasion,large cell carcinoma,lung cancer,Lung Neoplasms,Male,Mice Nude,Middle Aged,Myofibroblasts,Neoplasm Invasiveness,Oxidative Stress,Paracrine Communication,Phenotype,senescence,Signal Transduction,Time Factors,Tumor Microenvironment}
